  - m_Id: 10606215174701056
    m_Localized: Factory Basics
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267001
    m_Localized: Unlocks component factories. Produces machine parts from iron ingots,
      electronic components from copper and aluminum ingots, and precision tools
      from steel ingots and machine parts. Core mid-game production for vehicles and
      advanced industry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267002
    m_Localized: Unlocks general mines. Extracts iron ore, coal, copper ore, and aluminum
      ore. Does not produce gold ore—research Gold Mine Construction separately.
      High build and upkeep costs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267003
    m_Localized: Unlocks chemical plants. Consumes crude oil to produce fabric, complementing
      sawmill wood chains and reducing reliance on timber alone.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267004
    m_Localized: Unlocks heavy factories. Produces premium clothing from fabric and
      gold ore, and premium furniture from premium wood, fabric, and machine parts.
      High investment for luxury markets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267005
    m_Localized: Unlocks oil pumps. Extracts crude oil underground. Very high upkeep;
      foundation for chemical plants and fuel-using production. Completing this
      research unlocks chemical processing research.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267006
    m_Localized: Unlocks smelters. Converts iron, copper, and aluminum ores into ingots
      and gold ore into pure gold. Essential for metal and electronics chains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267007
    m_Localized: Unlocks engine factories. Produces engines from machine parts, electronic
      components, and steel ingots. Prerequisite for vehicle assembly.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267008
    m_Localized: Unlocks military factories. Produces small arms, heavy arms, and munitions
      using steel, machine parts, fine wood, and coal depending on the product.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267009
    m_Localized: Unlocks vehicle assembly plants. Produces cars, fighter jets, and
      battle tanks from engines, steel, electronics, aluminum, oil, and weapons.
      Highest-value but most complex chain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10166970572226560
    m_Localized: Foundation research for factory operations. Unlocks the Light Factory
      and Load station. Also opens research paths for mining, smelting, and oil
      extraction.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22606259738263552
    m_Localized: Unlock Building
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22606455687757824
    m_Localized: Raw Resource Search
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22606619886370816
    m_Localized: Production Efficiency
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266010
    m_Localized: Forest Survey I
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267010
    m_Localized: Surveys forest resources and raises how many logging camps you can
      place.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266011
    m_Localized: Forest Survey II
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267011
    m_Localized: Deeper timber assessment. Further increases logging camp capacity.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266012
    m_Localized: Forest Survey III
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267012
    m_Localized: Detailed watershed and yield mapping. More sites cleared for camps.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266013
    m_Localized: Forest Survey IV
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267013
    m_Localized: Advanced inventory and access routes. Expands sustainable extraction.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266014
    m_Localized: Forest Survey V
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267014
    m_Localized: Full regional survey network. Maximizes allowed logging camp footprint.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266015
    m_Localized: Mineral Survey I
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267015
    m_Localized: Exploration expands how many mines you can place for ore and minerals.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266016
    m_Localized: Mineral Survey II
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267016
    m_Localized: Better vein models and sampling. Further raises mine placement cap.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266017
    m_Localized: Mineral Survey III
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267017
    m_Localized: Deeper geology surveys open more viable mine sites on the map.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266018
    m_Localized: Mineral Survey IV
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267018
    m_Localized: Integrated reserve estimates and logistics. More parallel operations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266019
    m_Localized: Mineral Survey V
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267019
    m_Localized: Full district-scale mapping. Maximizes how many mines you may run.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266020
    m_Localized: Oil Survey I
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267020
    m_Localized: Seismic and field work increase allowed oil pump installations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266021
    m_Localized: Oil Survey II
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267021
    m_Localized: Refined subsurface models unlock more pump deployment slots.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266022
    m_Localized: Oil Survey III
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267022
    m_Localized: Extended appraisal wells and regional correlation. Higher cap.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266023
    m_Localized: Oil Survey IV
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267023
    m_Localized: Advanced reservoir characterization. More concurrent pumps allowed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266024
    m_Localized: Oil Survey V
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267024
    m_Localized: Basin-wide exploration program. Maximizes oil pump placement limit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266025
    m_Localized: Gold Vein Survey I
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267025
    m_Localized: Outcrop and sampling work to raise the gold mine placement limit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266026
    m_Localized: Gold Vein Survey II
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267026
    m_Localized: Stronger assays and geological models further expand placement caps.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266027
    m_Localized: Gold Vein Survey III
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267027
    m_Localized: Deep-targeted surveys scale up concurrent gold mining operations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266028
    m_Localized: Gold Vein Survey IV
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267028
    m_Localized: Reserve estimation and logistics analysis raise parallel mining limits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226266029
    m_Localized: Gold Mine Construction
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226267029
    m_Localized: Unlocks dedicated gold mines. Extracts gold ore only for smelting
      into pure gold. Requires prior mining research.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
